E%20and%20moved%20to%20Rhode%20Island%20at%208.%20My%20twin%20sister%20and%20I%20didn't%20speak%20English%20and%20were%20two%20of%20only%20three%20Asian%20kids%20at%20school.%20Even%20before%20I%20understood%20the%20words%2C%20I%20could%20tell%20people%20were%20making%20fun%20of%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20our%20parents%20didn't%20let%20us%20speak%20Chinese%20at%20home%20so%20that%20we'd%20learn%20English%20faster.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20when%20I%20could%20barely%20write%20my%20own%20name%2C%20they%20panicked%20and%20had%20us%20relearn%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20started%20at%20Duke%20University%2C%20I%20was%20shocked%20by%20how%20many%20Asian%20students%20there%20were.%20I%20was%20used%20to%20being%20the%20only%20one%20in%20the%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20majored%20in%20economics%20but%20discovered%20theater%20along%20the%20way%2C%20and%20chose%20to%20make%20it%20my%20minor.%20That's%20how%20I%20realized%20how%20much%20I%20loved%20being%20onstage%2C%20telling%20stories%2C%20and%20connecting%20with%20an%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20summer%20after%20freshman%20year%2C%20I%20returned%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-china-after-graduation-mit-manufacturing-shenzhen-schwarzman-sparrows-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChina%20to%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20ancient%20Chinese%20and%20was%20amazed%20at%20how%20much%20had%20changed%20since%20I%20had%20left%20the%20country%20in%201999.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ff15169-8b2d-4856-9f4a-ea634aef54a3%5C%22%3EFrom%20banking%20to%20acting%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduation%2C%20I%20applied%20for%20jobs%20in%20New%20York%20and%20got%20hired%20as%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-wall-street-investment-banking-after-fainting-bad-work-culture-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einvestment%20banking%20analyst%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20my%20boss%20if%20I%20could%20take%20one%20acting%20class%20a%20wee