20startup%20is%20cooperating%20with%20the%20OLSE%20to%20provide%20the%20information%20they%20need%20and%20that%20Scale%20AI%20is%20fully%20compliant%20with%20local%20laws%20and%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESan%20Francisco's%20investigation%20into%20Scale%20AI%20is%20limited%20to%20city%20residents%20who%20worked%20for%20the%20startup%20%E2%80%94%20including%20remotely%20%E2%80%94%20over%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20according%20to%20a%20now-deleted%20notice%20posted%20by%20Maura%20Prendiville%2C%20a%20compliance%20officer%20at%20the%20OLSE%2C%20in%20a%20subreddit%20for%20Outlier%20AI%2C%20a%20gig%20work%20platform%20run%20by%20Scale%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20notice%20didn't%20specify%20what%20types%20of%20labor%20practices%20the%20city%20is%20investigating%2C%20it%20did%20mention%20that%20investigators%20are%20looking%20to%20speak%20to%20people%20who%20worked%20for%20Scale%20AI%20as%20%26quot%3Btaskers%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bfreelancers%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20the%20startup's%20full-time%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation's%20existence%20doesn't%20mean%20Scale%20AI%20has%20broken%20the%20law%2C%20and%20the%20city%20could%20find%20it%20in%20favor%20of%20Scale%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20or%20drop%20its%20probe%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20OLSE%20declined%20to%20answer%20further%20questions%20about%20the%20probe%2C%20citing%20its%20policy%20of%20not%20commenting%20on%20ongoing%20investigations.%20The%20agency%20has%20the%20authority%20to%20levy%20fines%20for%20labor%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Reddit%20post%2C%20Prendiville%20specified%20that%20San%20Francisco%20is%20seeking%20to%20speak%20to%20people%20who%20worked%20for%20Scale%20AI%20through%20Outlier%20AI%20and%20Smart%20Ecosystem%2C%20another%20Scale%20AI%20platform.%20She%20also%20wrote%20that%20she%20seeks%20to%20speak%20with%20people%20who%20worked%20for%20Scale%20AI%20through%20HireArt%2C%20a%20third-party%20hiring%20agency%2C%20and%20the%20gig%20work%20marketplace%20Upwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpwork%20said%20it%20has%20not%20been%20contacted%20by%20OLSE.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWorker%20classification%20and%20compliance%20with%20labor%20regulations%20are%20ultimately%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20hiring%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Upwork%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20general%20matter%2C%20Upwork%20does%20not%20play%20a%20role%20in%20those%20determinations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMontalvo%2C%20the%20Scale%20AI%20spokesperson%2C%20said%20that%20the%20feedback%20the%20company%20gets%20from%20its%20contributors%20is%20%26quot%3Boverwhelmingly%20positive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20dedicated%20teams%20work%20hard%20to%20ensure%20contributors%20are%20paid%20fairly%2C%20feel%20supported%2C%20and%20can%20access%20the%20flexible%20earning%20opportunities%20they%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Scale%20AI%20has%20been%20investigated%20by%20labor%20regulators.%20It%20was%20also%20the%20subject%20of%20a%20federal%20Department%20of%20Labor%20investigation%20that%20was%20dropped%20this%20summer%2C%20TechCrunch%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2025%2F05%2F09%2Fthe-department-of-labor-just-dropped-its-investigation-into-scale-ai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20Scale%20AI%20workers%20have%20previously%20alleged%20that%20the%20company%20illegally%20underpaid%20them%2C%20denied%20them%20benefits%20like%20sick%20leave%2C%20and%20misclassified%20them%20as%20contractors%20in%20two%20lawsuits%20filed%20over%20the%20past%20year%20in%20San%20Francisco's%20superior%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20declined%20to%20comment.%20HireArt%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Acrollet%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu