ards%20affordable%2C%20year-round%20housing%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20correct%20the%20area's%20affordable%20housing%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCape%20Cod%20is%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20housing%20crisis%20that%20threatens%20the%20fabric%20of%20our%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20Barnstable%20County%20Assembly%20of%20Delegates%20Deputy%20Speaker%20Daniel%20Gessen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.capecod.gov%2F2025%2F09%2F04%2Fassembly-announces-september-24-special-hearing-on-transfer-fee%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThis%20legislative%20timeline%20is%20the%20scaffolding%20for%20the%20assembly%20to%20begin%20confronting%20the%20depth%20of%20this%20crisis%20and%20moving%20toward%20solutions%20that%20match%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20challenge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarnstable%20County%2C%20where%20Cape%20Cod%20is%20located%2C%20is%20generally%20a%20well-off%20region.%20But%20statistics%20show%20a%20significant%20wealth%20gap.%20The%20median%20household%20income%20is%20%2489%2C893%2C%20according%20to%20the%20US%20Census%2C%20only%20slightly%20higher%20than%20the%20national%20median%20of%20%2477%2C719.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20median%20home%20sale%20price%20in%20Barnstable%20County%20was%20%24730%2C000%20in%20July%2C%20well%20above%20the%20%24442%2C992%20national%20median%2C%20according%20to%20Redfin.%20And%20in%20enclaves%20like%20Chatham%2C%20Massachusetts%2C%20a%20town%20on%20the%20southeastern%20tip%20of%20Cape%20Cod%2C%20the%20median%20home%20sale%20price%20was%20%241%2C142%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225352%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Homes%20on%20the%20water%20in%20Cape%20Cod.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68bf3fbf57d362d375e7c1b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223264%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHomes%20on%20the%20water%20in%20Cape%20Cod.%3Cp%3ETetra%20Images%2FChris%20Hackett%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EA%20family%20today%20must%20earn%20more%20than%20double%20the%20average%20income%20just%20to%20afford%20the%20price%20of%20an%20average%20home.%20That's%20not%20just%20unsustainable.%20That%20is%20a%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20Gessen%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tax%2C%20which%20so%20far%20as%20a%20strong%20well%20of%20support%20from%20business%20leaders%2C%20county%20officials%2C%20housing%20advocates%2C%20and%20the%20Cape%20Cod%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%2C%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20way%20to%20revive%20the%20county's%20dwindling%20middle%20class.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BNearly%2030%25%20of%20the%20region's%20workforce%20now%20commutes%20to%20the%20Cape%20each%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Cape%20Cod%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20%3C%2Fspan%3ECEO%20Paul%20Niedzwiecki%20told%20Realtor.com.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20going%20to%20turn%20into%20something%20very%20different%20if%20we%20don't%20make%20aggressive%20and%20transformative%20moves%20to%20protect%20the%20middle%20class.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20news%20of%20the%20potential%20tax%2C%20Cape%20Cod%20real%20estate%20agent%20and%20full-time%20resident%20Alfred%20Schofield%20has%20already%20been%20fielding%20calls%20of%20panic%20from%20his%20wealthier%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20getting%20some%20calls%20from%20anxious%20sellers%2C%26quot%3B%20Schofield%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20there's%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20general%20trepidation%20from%20the%20affluent%20marketplace%20about%20the%20potential%20impacts%2C%20and%20more%20and%20more%20people%20contemplating%20a%20potential%20sale%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchofield%20said%20that%20while%20some%20sellers%20are%20trying%20to%20jump%20the%20gun%20and%20close%20deals%20before%20any%20changes%20go%20into%20effect%2C%20others%20are%20digging%20their%20heels%20in%20and%20holding%20on%20to%20properties%20longer%2C%20waiting%20for%20the%20dust%20to%20settle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20thinks%20that%20sellers%20will%20try%20their%20best%20to%20pass%20those%20extra%20costs%20on%20to%20the%20buyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20certainly%20will%20be%20people%20who%20try%20to%20bake%20those%20costs%20into%20the%20retail%20price%20of%20their%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20exactly%20positive%20of%20what%20the%20market%20impact%20would%20be%2C%20but%20I%20could%20certainly%20see%20a%20scenario%20where%20home%20prices%20rise%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20tax%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Rhode%20Island%2C%20lawmakers%20have%20already%20started%20charging%20wealthy%20vacationers%20with%20%26quot%3BThe%20Taylor%20Swift%20Tax%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20taxes%20second%20homes%20%242.50%20for%20every%20%24500%20in%20assessed%20value%20over%20%241%20million.%20The%20pop%20star%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-taylor-swifts-17-million-rhode-island-mansion-2016-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebought%20a%20home%20in%20Rhode%20Island%20for%20%2417.75%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Westerly%2C%20Rhode%20Island%2C%20property%20records%20show%20it's%20currently%20assessed%20at%20about%20%2428.3%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222191%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taylor%20Swift%20also%20has%20a%20house%20in%20Rhode%20Island.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dbac3e1f51cc001969fc73%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221368%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETaylor%20Swift%20also%20has%20a%20house%20in%20Rhode%20Island.%3Cp%3EGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Barnstable%20County%20proposal%20doesn't%20single%20out%20second-home%20owners%20specifically%2C%20but%20there%20are%20quite%20a%20few%20of%20them%20there.%20According%20to%20a%202022%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftown.barnstable.m