20to%20take%20the%20public%20market%20plunge%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%20Gemini%20Space%20Station%2C%20a%20crypto%20exchange%20backed%20by%20the%20billionaire%20Winklevoss%20twins%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20go%20public%20later%20this%20week%2C%20and%2025-year-old%20ticket%20marketplace%20StubHub%20launched%20its%20IPO%20roadshow%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKlarna's%20IPO%20price%20represents%20a%20major%20markdown%20from%20its%20peak%20valuation%2C%20however.%20The%20company%20raised%20%24639%20million%20in%202021%20at%20a%20%2445.6%20billion%20valuation%2C%20but%20slashed%20its%20valuation%20a%20stunning%2085%25%20to%20%246.7%20billion%20the%20next%20year%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feuropean-fintech-is-breaking-records-but-clouds-on-the-horizon-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efintech%20sector%20stumbled%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20rising%20interest%20rates%20and%20worsening%20investor%20sentiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKlarna%20chairperson%20and%20former%20Sequoia%20Capital%20Michael%20Moritz%20criticized%20the%20company's%20other%20investors%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20shift%20in%20Klarna's%20valuation%20is%20entirely%20due%20to%20investors%20suddenly%20voting%20in%20the%20opposite%20manner%20to%20the%20way%20they%20voted%20for%20the%20past%20few%20years.%20The%20irony%20is%20that%20Klarna's%20business%2C%20its%20position%20in%20various%20markets%2C%20and%20its%20popularity%20with%20consumers%20and%20merchants%20are%20all%20stronger%20than%20at%20any%20time%20since%20Sequoia%20first%20invested%20in%202010%2C%26quot%3B%20Moritz%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20about%20the%20round.%20%26quot%3BEventually%2C%20after%20investors%20emerge%20from%20their%20bunkers%2C%20the%20stocks%20of%20Klarna%20and%20other%20first-rate%20companies%20will%20receive%20the%20attention%20they%20deserve.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKlarna%20debuts%20on%20the%20US%20market%20facing%20a%20number%20of%20headwinds%2C%20inc