o-return-to-office-two-days-a-week-125091001634_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fdeloitte-us-asks-india-employees-to-return-to-office-two-days-a-week-125091001634_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20top%20OpenAI%20exec%20dropped%20a%20treasure%20trove%20of%20numbers%20Wall%20Street%20was%20desperate%20to%20see%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223868%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22OpenAI%20CFO%20Sarah%20Friar%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c1b60557d362d375e7e858%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222901%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOpenAI%20CFO%20Sarah%20Friar%3Cp%3EMike%20Segar%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20is%20raising%20billions%20at%20a%20%24500%20billion%20valuation%2C%20attracting%20intense%20investor%20interest.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20CFO%20Sarah%20Friar%20spoke%20at%20Goldman's%20tech%20conference%20in%20San%20Francisco%20this%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere%20are%20the%20highlights%20of%20what%20she%20shared%20with%20the%20packed%20room%20of%20conferencegoers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Goldman%20Sachs%20tech%20conference%20is%20happening%20in%20San%20Francisco%20this%20week.%20The%20headliner%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-cfo-sarah-friar-cloud-giants-learning-on-our-dime-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20CFO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-cfo-warns-software-disruption-saas-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESarah%20Friar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20shared%20a%20ton%20of%20fascinating%20data%20on%20the%20AI%20startup's%20booming%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20attended%20the%20talk%20and%20compiled%20the%20highlights%20of%20her%20disclosures.%20The%20room%20was%20packed%20for%20her%20talk%20on%20Tuesday.%20Even%20the%20overflow%20room%20was%20full%2C%20with%20many%20analysts%20and%20investors%20sitting%20on%20the%20floor%20to%20watch.%20I've%20never%20seen%20so%20many%20loafers%20and%20crossed%20legs%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20is%20raising%20billions%20of%20dollars%20at%20a%20%24500%20billion%20valuation.%20Employees%20are%20also%20selling%20billions%20of%20dollars%20of%20stock.%20Investor%20interest%20in%20this%20company's%20performance%20is%20intense.%20Here's%20a%20taste%20of%20what%20Friar%20told%20Wall%20Street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20is%20roughly%20split%2070%2F30.%2070%25%20is%20the%20consumer%20business%2C%20and%2030%25%20enterprise.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChatGPT%20has%20roughly%20700%20million%20weekly%20average%20users%20on%20the%20consumer%20side%20of%20the%20business.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAbout%204%20million%20developers%20have%20built%20on%20the%20OpenAI%20platform.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20has%20amassed%20roughly%205%20million%20paid%20seats%20from%20ChatGPT%20business%20products.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company's%20total%20revenue%20will%20be%20roughly%20%2413%20billion%20this%20year%2C%20up%204X%20from%202024.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20spent%20roughly%20%242.6%20billion%20on%20computing%20resources%20to%20help%20it%20generate%20that%20%2413%20billion%20in%20revenue.%20And%20a%20lot%20of%20that%20is%20likely%20recurring%20revenue.%20%26quot%3BThat%20tells%20me%20to%20keep%20spending%2C%26quot%3B%20Friar%20told%20the%20crowd.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20new%20model%20picker%20technology%20built%20into%20OpenAI's%20GPT-5%20model%20has%20led%20to%20more%20users%20tapping%20into%20the%20company's%20reasoning%20capabilities.%20About%207%25%20of%20GPT-5%20is%20now%20reasoning%20workloads%2C%20versus%20about%202%25%20before%20the%20latest%20models%20launched.%20Among%20enterprise%20users%2C%20reasoning%20workloads%20are%20now%20about%2050%25%20of%20the%20total.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInference%20costs%20are%20falling.%20GPT-4's%20cost%20per%20token%20was%20about%20%2433.%20Now%2C%20GPT-5%20nano%2C%20a%20smalle