-spotify-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENetflix%3C%2Fa%3E%20starting%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter.%20The%20Amazon%20DSP%2C%20or%20demand-side%20platform%2C%20is%20a%20self-service%20software%20that%20lets%20advertisers%20plan%20and%20buy%20ads%20across%20Amazon's%20properties%20and%20other%20apps%20and%20websites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Amazon%20DSP%20is%20a%20direct%20competitor%20to%20The%20Trade%20Desk%2C%20a%20pure-play%20public%20adtech%20company.%20The%20rivalry%20between%20the%20pair%20has%20been%20heating%20up%20following%20years%20of%20quiet%20investment%20from%20Amazon%20as%20part%20of%20a%20strategy%20to%20eventually%20overtake%20The%20Trade%20Desk%20and%20Google%20to%20become%20the%20world's%20No.%201%20DSP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20has%20been%20elbowing%20in%20on%20key%20media%20partnerships%20that%20had%20given%20The%20Trade%20Desk%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0which%20is%20also%20a%20Netflix%20DSP%20partner%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0its%20edge%20in%20the%20fast-growing%20connected-TV%20space.%20Amazon%20recently%20signed%20similar%20deals%20with%20Roku%20and%20Disney%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20analysts%20at%20Morgan%20Stanley%20downgraded%20The%20Trade%20Desk's%20stock%20to%20equal-weight%20from%20overweight%20and%20pared%20down%20their%20price%20target%20for%20the%20stock%20to%20%2450%20from%20%2480.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20note%20to%20clients%20sent%20before%20the%20Netflix%20deal%20was%20announced%2C%20Morgan%20Stanley's%20analysts%20cited%20%26quot%3Blingering%20execution%20concerns%2C%20softness%20in%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-open-web-decline-ads-publishers-doj-court-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopen%20web%20ad%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20intensifying%20competition%20in%20CTV%2C%26quot%3B%20noting%20the%20recent%20growth%20of%20Amazon%20DSP%20specifically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-trade-desk-shares-fell-comp