rted%20clearing%20their%20fields%20and%20some%20threw%20them%20on%20roads%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20Interestingly%2C%20Hrushikesh%20picked%20the%20discarded%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20and%20planted%20them%20in%20his%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%20took%20him%20on%20a%20path%20which%20led%20him%20to%20establishing%2C%20what%20is%20today%2C%20a%20multi-crore%20company!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hrushikesh%20started%20by%20planting%204%2C000%20discarded%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20on%20his%20field.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360102%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHrushikesh%20started%20by%20planting%204%2C000%20discarded%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20in%20his%20field.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELife%20in%20the%20drought-prone%20village%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaised%20in%20a%20humble%20family%20of%20farmers%2C%20Hrushikesh%20owned%20eight%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20Padali%20village.%20The%20family%20had%20traditionally%20been%20growing%20crops%20like%20paddy%2C